{"type": "article", "id": 27740, "title": "Gucci秀场坐垫也成爆款，以及，资生堂收购Laura Mercier｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-03T11:59:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 25286, "name": "唇彩"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 15755, "name": "走秀"}, {"id": 14934, "name": "刺绣"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 9879, "name": "胶囊系列"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 28551, "name": "Champion"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 3968, "name": "P&G"}, {"id": 17749, "name": "yeezy"}, {"id": 1099, "name": "资生堂"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 5065, "name": "Olivier Rousteing"}, {"id": 726, "name": "Pharrell Williams"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 106, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125233XnapIZoQ2lMA8Osx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/color-cosmetics/shiseido-acquires-laura-mercier-revive-10442801/\"><b>资生堂收购 Laura Mercier、ReVive</b></a>｜资生堂（Shiseido ）美国集团近日宣布收购 Laura Mercier、ReVive 品牌所有者 Gurwitch Products，预计支付 2.6 亿美元。预估 2015 年，彩妆艺术家品牌 Laura Mercier 以及奢侈护肤品牌 ReVive 净销售额分别为 1.6 亿、1500 万美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/P-G-appoints-David-S-Taylor-as-Chairman-of-the-Board-of-Directors,699493.html\"><b>宝洁任命新董事会主席</b></a>｜宝洁公司（P&amp;G）宣布 David S. Taylor 将担任董事长，7 月 1 日生效，Taylor 于 1980 年加入宝洁，协助建立了宝洁的婴儿护理、家庭护理、护发等核心业务。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Under-Armour-appoints-Tim-Coppens-as-Executive-Creative-Director,699488.html#.V1DfdoQrJQY\"><b>UA 任命 Tim Coppens 为新产品线创意总监</b></a>｜Under Armour 周四宣布将创立新产品线 Under Armour Sportswear，并任命 Tim Coppens 担任 Under Armour Sportswear  执行创意总监，预计将在今年秋季发布，包含男女装、鞋类和配饰。Tim Coppens  于 2011 年建立个人同名品牌，强调运动风，曾入围 CFDA/Vogue 时尚基金奖及 LVMH 大奖。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/eye/parties/pharrell-williams-opens-g-star-raw-fifth-avenue-location-10442208/\"><b>Pharrell Williams 开 G-Star Raw 新店</b></a>｜作为 G-Star 共同所有人的 Pharrell Williams，近日举办派对及自行车骑行活动庆祝第五大道 G-Star Raw 新旗舰店开幕，是全美最大  G-Star 门店。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/adidas-originals-yeezy-boost-release-date-june-2016\"><b>Yeezy 鞋 6 月 11 日发布</b></a>｜adidas Originals 在 Twitter 上公布 Yeezy Boost 第二季的发布日期为 6 月 11 日。据悉，还将包括高跟鞋、长靴系列。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Christian-Louboutin-launches-new-Loubilaque-lipstick-range,699612.html#.V1DiFYQrJQY\"><b>Christian Louboutin 发布新唇膏系列</b></a>｜“红底鞋”Christian Louboutin 再次发布一个新唇膏系列 “Loubilaque”，将在夏季上市，有从裸色至大红的 8 种色号。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125217kf8RL7PG4B3XKyFr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66470588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/resort-2017/new-york/red-valentino/review/\"> Red Valentino 发布 2017 度假系列</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125218xM4mrIW0Ps7R3YQ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125218htKQ2NJmMXBnCe6Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125219PI6Re9wYDBUvlA80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125219SEX9MImhP4o3FTLV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125220R2zU5emIghcpf9Ka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125220szvaj5FgZqX2yxrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>日本百货 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/beams-champion-collection-2016\">BEAMS 与 Champion  再次合作夏季胶囊系列</a>，包括卫衣、T 恤、慢跑裤等，灰色主色调，六月底上市：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125221R0sCF9rcnuIJZHYj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125221VPiY7R5lXQ6uGpbK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125222rEDUxs3oYXFZ15RT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125222jOLcr0wVCHQDZmhE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125223uWrYOdIao1ncih50.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021252232OEALCe6R1WklbsS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Gucci 在伦敦威斯敏斯特大教堂（Westminster Abbey ）<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/gucci-cruise-resort-alessandro-michele-westminster-abbey10442613-10442613/\">发布 2017 年度假系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125224fTdMuIWiStR1ajFs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125224ZjsS3rxcHdRpEBMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125225ip9Ra0ytwu1XLGHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125225hWQwE5A9rJq6Fcgy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125226K7x1b6HjGORLpJIF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212522642GyZzxUYHFRdJfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125227RWV1cgXwUGknpfvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021252279DO5zx4slJn20XtR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125228fAuQ0DEbe8jJnTpZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">此外，Gucci 在秀场为来宾准备的绿色天鹅绒坐垫，作为秀场礼物，有 Gucci 这几季标志性的刺绣图案，比如蛇、蜜蜂、蝴蝶、老虎等，在 Instagram 上引起广泛关注：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125228qEZNiGSulzPyYkaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63429138\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125229vTLF9SQPDgN0lXW8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">NikeLab 与 Olivier Rousteing 的联名系列今天发布，Cristiano Ronaldo 出镜，这里是广告大片：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125229JnGWBjvsqwSYMltE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125230p89bxy2VwcCn04FW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125231uf8j5abVPKlT0y9g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/luxury/womens-style/new-burberry-campaign-celebrates-the-best-of-british-featuring-e/\">Burberry 发布 2016 年秋冬的新广告</a>，插画与摄影结合，同时开启“即看即买”模式，广告发布之际，所有的包袋也都可以在门店购买：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125231W7v5nguQKpyosMrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125231Cnt8L10jrFDwPbg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125232167r4vxeVXbpjFk8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125232WkMxh6dwumSl0gL3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}